    <div class="divider reveal"></div>
    <p class="reveal">Ladla Pub &amp; Restaurant is a beloved local spot in the heart of Puttalam. We bring together the warmth of Sri Lankan hospitality with great food and a full drinks menu — a place to relax, celebrate, and enjoy yourself.</p>
